# Product Boundaries

AQLIYA products have separate boundaries:

AuditOS:
- audit workflow, trial balance, mapping, statements, notes, evidence, findings, review, approval, audit trail
- never claim full autonomous audit
- AI drafts, humans approve

LocalContentOS:
- local content intelligence and publishing workflow
- do not mix with AuditOS evidence model unless through shared platform primitives

DecisionOS:
- decision workflows, tenders, evidence-linked decisions
- not a generic CRM

SalesOS:
- sales intelligence and pipeline support
- not a full CRM unless explicitly requested
- keep data model controlled and staged

SimulationOS:
- currently marketing/future unless real implementation exists

AQLIYA Intelligence Core:
- shared governance, evidence, activity, audit logs, AI execution, review/approval, task center, platform signals

When editing:
- State affected product.
- Do not rename products casually.
- Do not move routes without checking `docs/source-of-truth/ROUTE_STRATEGY.md`.
